  "description": "",
  "guidelines": {
    "_rawHtml": "\n    <div class=\"guide-card\">\n      <div class=\"guide-section\">\n        <div class=\"guide-title\">Question Card</div>\n        <div class=\"guide-body\">AIがユーザーに質問を提示し回答を収集するカードコンポーネントです。Collapsed（none）状態とExpanded状態に分かれ、Expanded時にはChip Horizontal / Chip Default(2-col) / List Defaultの3種類の選択方式をサポートします。ChoiceResultCard内でも活用されます。</div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"guide-section\">\n        <div class=\"guide-subtitle\">Collapsed — incomplete / completed (var(--sizing-1400))</div>\n        <div style=\"margin-top:var(--spacing-200);display:flex;gap:var(--spacing-300);flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n          <div class=\"qcard qcard--collapsed\" style=\"width:var(--size-card-width-lg);background:linear-gradient(9.5deg, var(--color-gradient-background-ai-surface-stop-1) 5.1%, var(--color-gradient-background-ai-surface-stop-2) 92.36%)\">\n            <span data-ds-icon=\"chat-lines_solid\" data-ds-size=\"24\" data-ds-color=\"var(--color-content-primary)\"></span>\n            <span class=\"qcard__collapse-title\">Text</span>\n            <button class=\"qcard__collapse-btn\"><span data-ds-icon=\"chevron-down_solid\" data-ds-size=\"20\" data-ds-color=\"var(--color-content-primary)\"></span></button>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"qcard qcard--collapsed\" style=\"width:var(--size-card-width-lg);background:linear-gradient(9.5deg, var(--color-gradient-background-ai-surface-stop-1) 5.1%, var(--color-gradient-background-ai-surface-stop-2) 92.36%)\">\n            <span data-ds-icon=\"check-circle_solid\" data-ds-size=\"24\" data-ds-color=\"var(--color-content-success)\"></span>\n            <span class=\"qcard__collapse-title qcard__collapse-title--done\">Text</span>\n            <button class=\"qcard__collapse-btn\"><span data-ds-icon=\"chevron-down_solid\" data-ds-size=\"20\" data-ds-color=\"var(--color-content-primary)\"></span></button>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"guide-section\">\n        <div class=\"guide-subtitle\">chip horizontal — flex-wrap chip group</div>\n        <div style=\"margin-top:var(--sizing-200);\">\n          <div class=\"qcard qcard--expanded\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(42.63deg, var(--color-gradient-background-ai-surface-stop-1) 5.1%, var(--color-gradient-background-ai-surface-stop-2) 92.36%)\">\n            <div class=\"qcard__q-area\">\n              <div class=\"qcard__q-container\">\n                <div class=\"qcard__q-header\">\n                  <span data-ds-icon=\"question-text-circle_solid\" data-ds-size=\"24\" data-ds-color=\"var(--color-content-key)\"></span>\n                  <div class=\"qcard__q-text\"><div class=\"qcard__q-title\">Text</div></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"qcard__chips-h\">\n                  <button class=\"qcard__chip\">Label</button><button class=\"qcard__chip\">Label</button><button class=\"qcard__chip\">Label</button><button class=\"qcard__chip\">Label</button><button class=\"qcard__chip\">Label</button><button class=\"qcard__chip\">Label</button>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"qcard__input\"><span data-ds-icon=\"pen_solid\" data-ds-size=\"20\" data-ds-color=\"var(--color-content-tertiary)\"></span><span class=\"qcard__input-text\">Placeholder</span></div>\n              <div class=\"qcard__ghost-area\"><div class=\"qcard__ghost-row\"><span data-ds-icon=\"bulb_outline\" data-ds-size=\"20\" data-ds-color=\"var(--color-content-tertiary)\"></span><span class=\"qcard__ghost-label\">Ghost button</span><span data-ds-icon=\"chevron-down_solid\" data-ds-size=\"20\" data-ds-color=\"var(--color-content-tertiary)\"></span></div></div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"qcard__btn-wrap\"><button class=\"qcard__btn\">Label</button></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"guide-section\">\n        <div class=\"guide-subtitle\">chip default — 2-column grid</div>\n        <div style=\"margin-top:var(--sizing-200);\">\n          <div class=\"qcard qcard--expanded\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(42.63deg, var(--color-gradient-background-ai-surface-stop-1) 5.1%, var(--color-gradient-background-ai-surface-stop-2) 92.36%)\">\n            <div class=\"qcard__q-area\">\n              <div class=\"qcard__q-container\">\n                <div class=\"qcard__q-header\">\n                  <span data-ds-icon=\"question-text-circle_solid\" data-ds-size=\"24\" data-ds-color=\"var(--color-content-key)\"></span>\n                  <div class=\"qcard__q-text\"><div class=\"qcard__q-title\">Text</div></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"qcard__chips-d\">\n                  <div class=\"qcard__chips-d-row\"><button class=\"qcard__chip qcard__chip--full\">Label</button><button class=\"qcard__chip qcard__chip--full\">Label</button></div>\n                  <div class=\"qcard__chips-d-row\"><button class=\"qcard__chip qcard__chip--full\">Label</button><button class=\"qcard__chip qcard__chip--full\">Label</button></div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"qcard__input\"><span data-ds-icon=\"pen_solid\" data-ds-size=\"20\" data-ds-color=\"var(--color-content-tertiary)\"></span><span class=\"qcard__input-text\">Placeholder</span></div>\n              <div class=\"qcard__ghost-area\"><div class=\"qcard__ghost-row\"><span data-ds-icon=\"bulb_outline\" data-ds-size=\"20\" data-ds-color=\"var(--color-content-tertiary)\"></span><span class=\"qcard__ghost-label\">Ghost button</span><span data-ds-icon=\"chevron-down_solid\" data-ds-size=\"20\" data-ds-color=\"var(--color-content-tertiary)\"></span></div></div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"qcard__btn-wrap\"><button class=\"qcard__btn\">Label</button></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"guide-section\">\n        <div class=\"guide-subtitle\">list default — scrollable list items</div>\n        <div style=\"margin-top:var(--sizing-200);\">\n          <div class=\"qcard qcard--expanded\" style=\"background:linear-gradient(59.67deg, var(--color-gradient-background-ai-surface-stop-1) 5.1%, var(--color-gradient-background-ai-surface-stop-2) 92.36%)\">\n            <div class=\"qcard__q-area\">\n              <div class=\"qcard__q-container\">\n                <div class=\"qcard__q-header\">\n                  <span data-ds-icon=\"question-text-circle_solid\" data-ds-size=\"24\" data-ds-color=\"var(--color-content-key)\"></span>\n                  <div class=\"qcard__q-text\"><div class=\"qcard__q-title\">Text</div></div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"qcard__list\">\n                  <div class=\"qcard__list-item\"><div class=\"qcard__list-title\">Title text</div><div class=\"qcard__list-sub\">Sub text</div></div>\n                  <div class=\"qcard__list-item\"><div class=\"qcard__list-title\">Title text</div><div class=\"qcard__list-sub\">Sub text</div></div>\n                  <div class=\"qcard__list-item\"><div class=\"qcard__list-title\">Title text</div><div class=\"qcard__list-sub\">Sub text</div></div>\n                </div>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"qcard__input\"><span data-ds-icon=\"pen_solid\" data-ds-size=\"20\" data-ds-color=\"var(--color-content-tertiary)\"></span><span class=\"qcard__input-text\">Placeholder</span></div>\n              <div class=\"qcard__ghost-area\"><div class=\"qcard__ghost-row\"><span data-ds-icon=\"bulb_outline\" data-ds-size=\"20\" data-ds-color=\"var(--color-content-tertiary)\"></span><span class=\"qcard__ghost-label\">Ghost button</span><span data-ds-icon=\"chevron-down_solid\" data-ds-size=\"20\" data-ds-color=\"var(--color-content-tertiary)\"></span></div></div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"qcard__btn-wrap\"><button class=\"qcard__btn\">Label</button></div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"guide-section\">\n        <div class=\"guide-subtitle\">Anatomy</div>\n        <div class=\"guide-body\">\n          <b>Container</b> — <code>qcard</code>: var(--size-card-width-lg) wide, border var(--border-width-100) var(--color-border-tertiary), radius var(--sizing-400). Background: purple→blue 0.06 opacity gradient (angle varies by type).<br>\n          <b>Collapsed</b> — <code>qcard--collapsed</code>: var(--sizing-1400) height, flex row, px var(--sizing-400). Icon (var(--sizing-600)) + title (var(--sizing-400) bold, flex:1) + chevron button (var(--sizing-800)).<br>\n          <b>Expanded</b> — <code>qcard--expanded</code>: flex column, gap var(--sizing-500), p var(--sizing-400).<br>\n          <b>Question header</b> — <code>qcard__q-area</code> > <code>qcard__q-container</code> (gap var(--sizing-300)) > <code>qcard__q-header</code>: icon (gradient circle) + <code>qcard__q-text</code> (title var(--sizing-400) bold + optional sub var(--font-size-0687)).<br>\n          <b>Chip Horizontal</b> — <code>qcard__chips-h</code>: flex-wrap, justify-center, gap var(--sizing-200).<br>\n          <b>Chip Default</b> — <code>qcard__chips-d</code>: flex column, gap var(--sizing-200). Each <code>qcard__chips-d-row</code>: flex row, gap var(--sizing-200). Chips use <code>qcard__chip--full</code> (flex:1).<br>\n          <b>Chip</b> — <code>qcard__chip</code>: h var(--sizing-1000), radius var(--border-radius-full), border var(--color-gradient-border-secondary-stop-1), bg white, var(--line-height-label-small), px var(--sizing-300).<br>\n          <b>List</b> — <code>qcard__list</code>: flex column, gap var(--sizing-200). Each <code>qcard__list-item</code>: border var(--color-gradient-border-secondary-stop-1), radius var(--sizing-200), px var(--sizing-400) py var(--sizing-300). Title var(--line-height-label-small) + Sub var(--sizing-300) rgba 0.56.<br>\n          <b>Text Input</b> — <code>qcard__input</code>: h var(--sizing-1000), border var(--color-gradient-border-secondary-stop-1), radius var(--sizing-200). Pen icon + placeholder text.<br>\n          <b>Ghost area</b> — <code>qcard__ghost-row</code>: bulb icon + bold label (rgba 0.56) + chevron.<br>\n          <b>Bottom Button</b> — <code>qcard__btn-wrap</code>: gradient bg wrapper (calc(var(--border-width-100) * 1.5) padding, radius var(--border-radius-full)). Inner <code>qcard__btn</code>: white bg, var(--sizing-1000) height, var(--line-height-label-small) bold var(--color-content-primary).\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div><!-- guide-card -->\n  "
  },
  "selector": ".qcard"
}